<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q32_v2" title="Q32_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      La siguiente es la resolución que hizo un estudiante para la ecuación
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>:
      <br />
      Paso 1:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      Paso 2:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      Paso 3:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>7</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      Paso 4:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      ¿En qué paso se cometió el primer error?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">En el paso 1.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En el paso 1 se suma <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> en ambos lados de <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que resulta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Esa transformación sí es válida.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">En el paso 2.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En el paso 2 solo se reducen términos semejantes: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pasa correctamente a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">En el paso 3.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Desde <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, para aislar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> se debe restar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> en ambos lados, obteniendo <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. El estudiante escribió <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y ese es el primer error.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">En el paso 4.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El primer error aparece antes. Si desde <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> se divide por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces sí se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso el paso 4 es coherente con el paso anterior; el problema está en el paso 3, donde debía quedar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Ecuación original</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Revisar el paso 1</strong></p>
            <p>El estudiante pasa a:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Eso es correcto, porque equivale a sumar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Y en el lado derecho:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Revisar el paso 2</strong></p>
            <p>El estudiante pasa a:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>También es correcto, porque:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Revisar el paso 3</strong></p>
            <p>Desde</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>para despejar, se debe restar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces queda:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>y no</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, el primer error está en el paso 3.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Resolver correctamente la ecuación</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Ahora dividimos ambos lados por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La primera equivocación ocurre en el paso 3, así que la alternativa correcta es la C.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>